```py
>>> from io import StringIO
>>> import numpy as np 
```

```py
>>> s = StringIO(u"1,1.3,abcde")
>>> data = np.genfromtxt(s, dtype=[('myint','i8'),('myfloat','f8'),
... ('mystring','S5')], delimiter=",")
>>> data
array((1, 1.3, b'abcde'),
 dtype=[('myint', '<i8'), ('myfloat', '<f8'), ('mystring', 'S5')]) 
```
